                      },
                      "width": "70%",
                    },
                    {
                      "body": {
                        "__richtext_html": "<p>Fly, surf, ski, all within an hour away. Plus every business partner is around the corner.<br></p>",
                      },
                      "body_role": "text14",
                      "kind": "text",
                      "width": "30%",
                    },
                  ],
                },
                {
                  "kind": "subgrid",
                  "subgrid": [
                    {
                      "body": {
                        "__richtext_html": "<p>Day or night, Burbank delights with vibrant energy and one-of-a-kind character.</p>",
